<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA511_04_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema511_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema511_04_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">
          두 식&nbsp;<i class="ex1">가</i>와&nbsp;<i class="ex1">나</i>를 각각 계산하고, 계산 결과를 비교해 봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">두 식이 어떻게 다른지 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box">
              <span class="flex align_center gap_12"><i class="ex1">가</i>34-2×4+6</span>
              <span class="flex align_center gap_12"><i class="ex1">나</i>34-2×(4+6)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box ex">
                <p>식<i class="ex1">가</i>는 (&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)가 없고, 식<i class="ex1">나</i>는 (&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)가 있습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y">두 점을 선택하여 두 식의 계산 순서를 나타내고, 계산해 봅시다.</h3>
            <div class="compair">
              <div class="compair_inwrap">
                <div class="input_area dir_col">
                  <div class="question_box">
                    <span class="flex align_center gap_12"><i class="ex1">가</i>34-2×4+6=</span>
                    <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="32"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="drawing_area area1" data-dot-count="4" data-answer-single="[[2,3],[1,23],[4,123]]">
                    <svg class="connection_lines"></svg>
                    <!-- 선을 그릴 SVG -->
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="input_area dir_col">
                  <div class="question_box">
                    <span class="flex align_center gap_12"><i class="ex1">나</i>34-2×(4+6)=</span>
                    <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="drawing_area area2" data-dot-count="4" data-answer-single="[[3,4],[2,34],[1,234]]">
                    <svg class="connection_lines"></svg>
                    <!-- 선을 그릴 SVG -->
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_3">
            <h3 lang="y">두 식의 계산 결과를 비교해 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="question_box">
              <span class="flex align_center gap_12"><i class="ex1">가</i>34-2×4+6</span>
              <span class="flex align_center gap_12"><i class="ex1">나</i>34-2×(4+6)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="question_box" lang="y">
              <span>(&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)가 없을 때에는</span>
              <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                <math-field data-answer-single="32"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>, (&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)가 있을 때에는</span>
              <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                <math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>로 두 식의 계산 결과는</span>
              <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="다릅니다.">
                  <option></option>
                  <option value="같습니다."></option>
                  <option value="다릅니다."></option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>